a Prix Space Race and get the Power Sphera named TrophyBot.\n}}\n{{Episode List\n|EpisodeNumber=16\n|Title=Looping Loopa\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|{{flagicon|MAS}} December 15, 2017}}\n|AltDate={{flagicon|INA}} December 24, 2017\n|ShortSummary=Admiral Tarung gives BoBoiBoy and his friends a break from TAPOPS work. They come back to Earth and decide to go for a picnic on the next day. Then they find a Power Sphere named LoopBot, having the powers to loop, which Adu Du wanted. BoBoiBoy and his friends must save LoopBot from Adu Du who wanted to do mischieves with his looping power!\n}}\n{{Episode List\n|EpisodeNumber=17\n|Title=Making Waves\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|{{flagicon|MAS}} December 22, 2017}}\n|AltDate={{flagicon|INA}} December 31, 2017\n|ShortSummary=The lava rock monster named Roktaroka came to Earth to get revenge from BoBoiBoy for destroying his house.\n}}\n{{Episode List\n|EpisodeNumber=18\n|Title=B.R.R.O.'s Revenge\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|{{flagicon|MAS}} December 29, 2017}}\n|AltDate={{flagicon|INA}} January 7, 2018\n|ShortSummary=In pursuit of BellBot, a robot called Accurate Ballistic Arrow Mercenary or A.B.A.M attacks Cattus' village. BoBoiBoy and his friends must travel to Gurunda once again to battle A.B.A.M and save Cattus' friends and family.\n}}\n{{Episode List\n|EpisodeNumber=19\n|Title=Copy and Paste\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|{{flagicon|MAS}} May 24, 2018}}\n|AltDate={{flagicon|INA}} May 26, 2018\n|ShortSummary=BoBoiBoy and his friends were on their way home to the TAPOPS Space Station after successfully completing a mission. However, on their way home they face problems and are forced to seek help on nearby planets. Unexpectedly, they had to deal with alien piracy criminal that were most wanted by TAPOPS.\n}}\n{{Episode List\n|EpisodeNumber=20\n|Title=Emotion Manipulation\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|{{flagicon|MAS}} May 31, 2018}}\n|AltDate={{flagicon|INA}} May 26, 2018\n|ShortSummary=After returning to the TAPOPS S